Aayush is correct, we've updated the tutorials page and are cleaning up some old examples.
That NMT tutorial is linked under 'Sequences' (there's another [NMT w/ attention](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/eager/python/examples/nmt_with_attention/nmt_with_attention.ipynb) using eager listed under 'Research and experimentation').

I added a redirect for '/tutorials/seq2seq' to fix the 404. It redirects back to the main tutorials page.
